# Netlify redirect rules. One per line: <source> <target> <status>
# https://docs.netlify.com/routing/redirects

# TestFlight public-beta shortcut.
# Apple's join URL is opaque (testflight.apple.com/join/<code>); this lets
# us share https://trymercurius.com/beta everywhere — Instagram, posters,
# QR codes — and keep the underlying TestFlight URL out of the public copy.
# 302 (temporary) because the join code rotates if the external-testing
# group is ever recreated; 301 would get aggressively cached and outlive
# the actual link.
# Netlify redirect matching is case-sensitive, so list the common-typed
# capitalizations explicitly (phones autocapitalize the first letter).
# /beta/ with a trailing slash is already handled by Netlify automatically.
/beta   https://testflight.apple.com/join/3ujBtDsa   302
/Beta   https://testflight.apple.com/join/3ujBtDsa   302
/BETA   https://testflight.apple.com/join/3ujBtDsa   302
